# Required modules
Email::Send::Gmail  ->  command: sudo cpan Email::Send::Gmail
MIME::Lite          ->  command: sudo cpan install MIME:Lite

#Install

(Run has root so recommend script placed in root home)

1. sudo apt-get install git
2. sudo cpan Email::Send::Gmail
3. sudo cpan install MIME:Lite
4. sudo -i
5. git clone https://github.com/SmileyMan/snapPERL.git
6. cd snapPERL
7. gedit/vi/nano Config (Modify setting to suit)
8. ./snapPERL.pl to confirm all runs ok
9. crontab -e
add 
    0 2 * * * ~/snapPERL/snapPERL.pl >/dev/null 2>&1 
to crontab and save (Run at 2am each day adjust has needed)
10. exit
